{"tid":2479513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓在野國民力量黨勝出首爾及釜山市長選舉","createTime":"2021-04-08T00:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T01:01:26.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"710540a0093870a70dc94d11f7550d2068c62f5e","tid":2479513,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:47:28.000Z","msg":"南韓的地方政府補選結束，其中首爾及釜山的市長選舉都由在野黨勝出。<br />\n<br />\n南韓中央選舉管理委員會指，代表在野國民力量黨參選首爾市長的吳世勛以百分之57.5得票，擊敗代表執政共同民主黨的候選人朴映宣，再度出任首爾市長。朴映宣承認落敗，說會虛心接受結果，又感謝選民支持。<br />\n<br />\n至於釜山市長選舉，國民力量黨的朴亨埈以近六成三票數擊敗共同民主黨的金榮春。<br />\n<br />\n今次選舉被視為下屆總統大選的前哨戰，而執政共同民主黨慘敗，將令餘下不足一年任期的總統文在寅成為「跛腳鴨總統」"},{"pid":"6f5daf7464d2bcaa890af6920ea7712407eb7306","tid":2479513,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=430260&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D430260%26home%3D1&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=79a7f1f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D430260%26home%3D1&h=6159fa81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=430260&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"e37fa81429085a0ebf0ad51df3c0f8816d1c9025","tid":2479513,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"奶定唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e49291b04e20e453840a5b11e68a145f79e4e7","tid":2479513,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e37fa81429085a0ebf0ad51df3c0f8816d1c9025","tid":2479513,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"奶定唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:01:26.000Z","msg":"呢方面野較難講<br />\n但親美反中傾向更大"}]}